strings: <voice_0x010014E8><se_low>King Trode: Medea? Whatever is the matter, my dear?
<voice_0x010014E9><se_high>Princess Medea: In the forest! A boy! He's<endash>
<voice_0x010014EA><se_low>King Trode: What? You haven't been walking alone in the forest again, have you? How many times have I warned you about that?
<voice_0x010014EB><se_high>Princess Medea: But the boy! He's sick. He's just lying on the ground. Please, we have to help him!
<voice_0x010014EC><se_low>King Trode: A boy? What boy? I think it would be best if you took a few deep breaths and started again from<endash>
<voice_0x010014ED><se_high>Princess Medea: No! We have to go at once or he could die!
